{"tid":1198114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【肅立】 鮮血遍地 魂魄飛逝 全為吾等自由","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T11:01:33.000Z","uid":154486,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d71df8a93d89c14fc8ba88ff278a1233049f2f","tid":1198114,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FNl5HyhhWwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFNl5HyhhWwg&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=dc72a256\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FNl5HyhhWwg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吾等烏克蘭   榮光猶在<br />\n自由尚存人間<br />\n吾等同胞   青天之上<br />\n命運再展笑顏<br />\n吾等強敵   去如朝露   終須消散<br />\n是以兄弟   吾等國土   將必歸屬吾身<br />\n<br />\n鮮血遍地   魂魄飛逝   <br />\n全為吾等自由<br />\n以此足證   吾等兄弟<br />\n皆為哥薩克民族！<br />\n<br />\n吾友奮起   血戰沙場<br />\n由桑水到頓河<br />\n茫茫我土   昭昭吾國<br />\n他人不可侵犯<br />\n浩浩黑海將展笑顏<br />\n滔滔聶伯終會歡騰<br />\n皆因吾等烏克蘭   昔日榮光再臨！<br />\n<br />\n鮮血遍地   魂魄飛逝   <br />\n全為吾等自由<br />\n以此足證   吾等兄弟<br />\n皆為哥薩克民族！"},{"pid":"bd26f5e6563ec3a4fd603dc47b325e80bd0e3a87","tid":1198114,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:48:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4736e079772b904c3590da4bb649fa5b6dc2ecb2","tid":1198114,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da439c330d150796fbc009660a07340566c68988","tid":1198114,"uid":886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*KnjgK3IXW3hFDbqWp-4x3g.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-images-1.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1600%2F1%2AKnjgK3IXW3hFDbqWp-4x3g.jpeg&h=669cb93a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cee83ba2de9798e1323f30d3b4f35c05bb44e4c","tid":1198114,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:04:50.000Z","msg":"人地本身已經話有民主<br />\n都要打生打死先有未來<br />\n<br />\n我地先岩岩